---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <section class="page-hero">
    <img 
      src="/images/tablet-smart-home.jpg" 
      alt="Smart home tablet interface" 
      class="hero-background" 
    />
    <div class="hero-content-overlay">
      <h1>What We Do</h1>
      <p>TechNest designs and installs smart technology for Chicagoland homes and small businesses, from security and WiFi to automation and connected systems that simply work.</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="hero-button">Get in touch</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="what-we-do-info">
    <div class="what-we-do-container">
      <p>TechNest helps homeowners and small businesses across Chicagoland design and install smart technology that makes spaces more secure, comfortable, and easy to manage. We focus on solutions that fit naturally into how you live or work, with clear guidance and reliable systems you can use with confidence.</p>
      
      <p>Our services include home security systems, smart home devices, WiFi improvements, automated lighting and entertainment setups, as well as business security, access control, network upgrades, and point of sale connectivity.</p>
      
      <p>From stronger WiFi to safer entry points and more connected spaces, TechNest delivers clean installation and dependable local support you can rely on.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="services-comparison">
    <div class="services-column services-column-light">
      <h2>Home Services</h2>
      <p>Your home should feel comfortable, secure, and easy to manage. TechNest helps homeowners across Chicagoland design and install smart home technology that works reliably and fits naturally into everyday life.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Smart home security with cameras and alarms</li>
        <li>Strong, reliable whole home WiFi and network improvements</li>
        <li>Home automation for lighting, comfort, and convenience</li>
        <li>Whole home audio and clean entertainment setups</li>
        <li>Clear guidance, professional installation, and long term local support</li>
      </ul>
      <a href="/contact" class="services-button services-button-primary">Learn More</a>
    </div>

    <div class="services-column services-column-blue">
      <h2>Small Business Services</h2>
      <p>Running a small business is demanding. TechNest supports businesses across Chicagoland with reliable, cost effective technology that improves security, strengthens connectivity, and keeps daily operations running smoothly.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Business security systems and surveillance cameras</li>
        <li>Access control for doors and restricted areas</li>
        <li>Network and WiFi upgrades for reliable performance</li>
        <li>Point of sale connectivity and system support</li>
        <li>Smart automation to reduce manual tasks</li>
        <li>Friendly, professional installation, and responsive local support</li>
      </ul>
      <a href="/contact" class="services-button services-button-secondary">Learn More</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-hero {
    position: relative;
    min-height: 60vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: flex-start;
    overflow: hidden;
    margin-top: 70px;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .hero-background {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center;
    z-index: 0;
  }

  .hero-content-overlay {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 10;
    background-color: #0072cc;
    padding: 2rem 2rem;
    max-width: 580px;
    margin-left: 2rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .hero-content-overlay h1 {
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem 0;
    color: #fafafa;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.1;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .hero-content-overlay p {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: #fafafa;
    margin: 0 0 2rem 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .hero-button {
    display: inline-block;
    background-color: #0052a3;
    color: #fafafa;
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 0.25rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 1rem;
    transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  .hero-button:hover {
    background-color: #003d7a;
  }

  .what-we-do-info {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5f7fa 0%, #f0f3f8 100%);
    background-image: url('/background-shapes.png');
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center;
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    background-attachment: fixed;
    padding: 6rem 2rem;
  }

  .what-we-do-container {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .what-we-do-container p {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: #0072cc;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin: 0 0 2.5rem 0;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .what-we-do-container p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .services-comparison {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    min-height: 100vh;
    grid-auto-rows: auto;
  }

  .services-column {
    padding: 4rem 3rem;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    grid-template-rows: auto auto auto auto;
    gap: 1rem;
    align-items: center;
    justify-items: center;
  }

  .services-column-light {
    background-color: #f5f7fa;
    background-image: url('/background-shapes.png');
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center;
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    background-attachment: fixed;
  }

  .services-column-blue {
    background-color: #0072cc;
  }

  .services-column h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin: 0;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .services-column-light h2 {
    color: #0072cc;
  }

  .services-column-blue h2 {
    color: #fafafa;
  }

  .services-column p {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin: 0;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .services-column-light p {
    color: #0072cc;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .services-column-blue p {
    color: #fafafa;
  }

  .services-column ul {
    list-style-position: inside;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    display: inline-block;
    text-align: left;
    align-self: center;
    justify-self: center;
  }

  .services-column li {
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
  }

  .services-column-light li {
    color: #0072cc;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .services-column-blue li {
    color: #fafafa;
  }

  .services-button {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 1rem 2.5rem;
    border-radius: 0.25rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
    border: 2px solid transparent;
    cursor: pointer;
    text-align: center;
    width: fit-content;
    justify-self: center;
  }

  .services-button-primary {
    background-color: #0072cc;
    color: #fafafa;
  }

  .services-button-primary:hover {
    background-color: #0052a3;
  }

  .services-button-secondary {
    background-color: #fafafa;
    color: #0072cc;
    border-color: #fafafa;
  }

  .services-button-secondary:hover {
    background-color: #f0f0f0;
  }

  .page-content {
    padding: 6rem 2rem;
  }

  .content-container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .content-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 3rem;
  }

  .content-item h2 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
    color: var(--accent-light);
  }

  .content-item p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .page-hero {
      min-height: 50vh;
    }

    .hero-content-overlay {
      max-width: 90%;
      padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
      margin-left: 1rem;
    }

    .hero-content-overlay h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .hero-content-overlay p {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .services-comparison {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      min-height: auto;
    }

    .services-column {
      padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
    }

    .services-column h2 {
      font-size: 1.75rem;
    }

    .services-column p {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .services-column li {
      font-size: 0.9375rem;
    }

    .what-we-do-info {
      padding: 3rem 1rem !important;
    }

    .what-we-do-container {
      padding: 0 !important;
    }

    .what-we-do-container p {
      font-size: 1rem !important;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem !important;
    }

    .page-content {
      padding: 4rem 1rem;
    }

    .content-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2rem;
    }
  }
</style>
